      <t>This document specifies general rules for the interaction between the BIER Algorithm (BAR) and the IGP Algorithm (IPA) used for underlay path calculation. The semantics defined in this document update RFC8401 and RFC8444. This document also updates the BIER Algorithm registry established in RFC8401.</t>
